question: Yashaswini Singh Deswal is associated to which city?
explanation: Young shooter Yashaswini Singh Deswal from Delhi has recently won gold in the women\'s 10m Air Pistol event at the ISSF World Cup at Rio de Janeiro in Brazil. With the win, she has also secured an Olympic quota for India. This is India\'s 9th quota in shooting for 2020 Tokyo Games. World no.1 Olena Kostevych of Ukraine claimed the silver, while Serbia\'s Jasmina Milavonovic bagged the bronze in the ongoing event.
